title: Karuzo
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Serves vegan/vegetarian cuisine like pasta and salad in addition to fish. Homemade seitan. Non-smoking. English spoken and on menu. Only 18 seats so reserve ahead. Directions: 1 minute walk from the Catholic Cathedral. Note Karuzo has a "bb" street address - it's at the east end of street before the numbering starts.
